Zardus looks at Nemesis Enforcer as the other enters. "Nemesis, this is 
Soundwave. Soundwave, Nemesis," he introduces the two bots.

"Soundwave is here on a mission of peace," Zardus says, looking back at 
Soundwave, "Take a seat. He's explaining who sent him."
